"One common cause of failures on macOS is the use of accessibility "
"technologies that are incompatible with the graphics toolkit calibre uses.  "
"Try turning off VoiceOver if you have it on. Also go to System "
"Preferences->System->Universal Access and turn off the setting for enabling "
"access for assistive devices in all the tabs. Another cause can be some "
